window.CONFIG = CONFIG;</script><meta name="generator" content="Hexo 6.3.0"></head><body><div class="container" id="container"><header class="header" id="header"><div class="header-inner header-inner--height header-inner--bgcolor"><nav class="header-nav header-nav--sticky"><div class="header-nav-inner"><div class="header-nav-menubtn"><i class="fas fa-bars"></i></div><div class="header-nav-menu"><div class="header-nav-menu-item"><a class="header-nav-menu-item__link" href="/"><span class="header-nav-menu-item__icon"><i class="fas fa-home"></i></span><span class="header-nav-menu-item__text">首页</span></a></div><div class="header-nav-menu-item"><a class="header-nav-menu-item__link" href="/archives/"><span class="header-nav-menu-item__icon"><i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i></span><span class="header-nav-menu-item__text">归档</span></a></div></div><div class="header-nav-mode"><div class="mode"><div class="mode-track"><span class="mode-track-moon"></span><span class="mode-track-sun"></span></div><div class="mode-thumb"></div></div></div></div></nav></div></header><main class="main" id="main"><div class="main-inner"><div class="content-wrap" id="content-wrap"><div class="content" id="content"><!-- Just used to judge whether it is an article page--><div id="is-post"></div><div class="post"><header class="post-header"><h1 class="post-title">Flask</h1><div class="post-meta"><span class="post-meta-item post-meta-item--createtime"><span class="post-meta-item__icon"><i class="far fa-calendar-plus"></i></span><span class="post-meta-item__info">发表于</span><span class="post-meta-item__value">2023-12-18</span></span><span class="post-meta-item post-meta-item--updatetime"><span class="post-meta-item__icon"><i class="far fa-calendar-check"></i></span><span class="post-meta-item__info">更新于</span><span class="post-meta-item__value">2023-12-18</span></span></div></header><div class="post-body"><p>Flask是python中非常流行的一个web框架，可以帮助开发人员快速构建Web应用程序。其实，说白了，就是搭建一个后台相应请求的处理程序。</p>
<p>一、基础部分<br>1.安装Flask</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install Flask</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<p>2.创建Flask应用</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from flask import Flask</span><br><span class="line"> app = Flask(__name__) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<p>3.创建视图函数（即界面）<br>&emsp;&emsp;创建视图函数并将其与 URL 绑定，以便在请求到达该 URL 时调用该视图函数并返回响应。在下面的示例中，我们创建了一个简单的视图函数 hello，并将其与根 URL（&#x2F;）绑定。当用户访问应用的根 URL 时，该函数将返回一个包含字符串“Hello, World!”的响应。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@app.route(&#x27;/&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line"> def hello():</span><br><span class="line">    return &#x27;Hello, World!&#x27; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<p>4.运行应用<br>&emsp;&emsp;这将在本地主机上的默认端口（5000）上启动 Flask 应用。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if __name__ == &#x27;__main__&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">    app.run() </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<p>二、进阶<br>1.创建可选视图<br>&emsp;&emsp;一个 url 地址和一个处理函数对应，就可以形成一个接口。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@app.route(&#x27;/index&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">def index():</span><br><span class="line">    return &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;msg&quot;: &quot;success&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;data&quot;: &quot;welcome to use flask.&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;如果还需要定义另外的接口，只需要参照上面的例子继续定义。 比如实现一个注册接口：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@app.route(&#x27;/user/&lt;u_id&gt;&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">def index(u_id):</span><br><span class="line">	return &#123;</span><br><span class="line">		&#x27;id&#x27;: u_id,</span><br><span class="line">		&#x27;msg&#x27;: &#x27;success&#x27;,</span><br><span class="line">		&#x27;data&#x27;: &#x27;welcome to use flask&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;这时访问需要 :5000&#x2F;user&#x2F;2, 意为u_id为2</p>
<p>2.调用模型，比如百川</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">def setup():</span><br><span class="line">    global tokenizer, bigmodels</span><br><span class="line">    model_path = &#x27;/home/ma-user/work/yz-gaoguangze/llm-model/Baichuan2-13B-Chat&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(model_path, use_fast=False, trust_remote_code=True)</span><br><span class="line">    bigmodel1 = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(model_path, device_map=&quot;cuda:0&quot;, torch_dtype=torch.bfloat16, trust_remote_code=True)</span><br><span class="line">    bigmodel1.generation_config = GenerationConfig.from_pretrained(model_path)</span><br><span class="line">    bigmodel2 = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(model_path, device_map=&quot;cuda:1&quot;, torch_dtype=torch.bfloat16, trust_remote_code=True)</span><br><span class="line">    bigmodel2.generation_config = GenerationConfig.from_pretrained(model_path)</span><br><span class="line">    bigmodels = [bigmodel1, bigmodel2]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 建立历史消息记录：字典形式，key为用户id，value为用户的历史消息</span><br><span class="line">def history_setup():</span><br><span class="line">    global history_messages</span><br><span class="line">    history_messages = dict()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 最基本的百川2 推理</span><br><span class="line">def inference(prompt):</span><br><span class="line">    global gpu_id</span><br><span class="line">    bigmodel = bigmodels[gpu_id % 2]</span><br><span class="line">    messages = []</span><br><span class="line">    messages.append(&#123;&quot;role&quot;: &quot;user&quot;, &quot;content&quot;: prompt&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    response = bigmodel.chat(tokenizer, messages)</span><br><span class="line">return response</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 实现文本完成任务：包括基础prompt 摘要，关键词提取，命名实体识别，事件抽取  </span><br><span class="line">@app.route(&#x27;/text-completion&#x27;, methods=[&#x27;POST&#x27;])</span><br><span class="line">def text_completion():</span><br><span class="line">    global gpu_id</span><br><span class="line">    gpu_id += 1</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    # 获取请求参数</span><br><span class="line">    input_text = request.json.get(&#x27;prompt&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">    model = request.json.get(&#x27;model&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">    user = request.json.get(&#x27;user&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">    is_stream = request.json.get(&#x27;stream&#x27;, False)</span><br><span class="line">    received_time = int(time.time())</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    def generate(messages):</span><br><span class="line">        position = 0</span><br><span class="line">        position = 0</span><br><span class="line">        index = 0  # 没用上</span><br><span class="line">        for response in bigmodels[gpu_id % 2].chat(tokenizer, messages, stream=True):</span><br><span class="line">            part_response = response[position:]</span><br><span class="line">            res = complete_template2(part_response, 0, received_time, finish_reason=&#x27;null&#x27;, id=&quot;example-completion-1&quot;, object=&quot;text-completion&quot;, model=model, system_fingerprint=&quot;example&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">            index += 1</span><br><span class="line">            position = len(response)</span><br><span class="line">            if torch.backends.mps.is_available():</span><br><span class="line">                torch.mps.empty_cache()</span><br><span class="line">            yield res</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">        yield complete_template2(&#x27;&#x27;, index, received_time, finish_reason=&#x27;stop&#x27;, id=&quot;example-completion-1&quot;, object=&quot;text-completion&quot;, model=model, system_fingerprint=&quot;example&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        yield &#x27;data: [DONE]&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    prompt_func = None</span><br><span class="line">    if model == &#x27;casia-abstract&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">        prompt_func = abstract_extract_prompt</span><br><span class="line">    elif model == &#x27;casia-keyword&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">        prompt_func = keyword_extract_prompt</span><br><span class="line">    elif model == &#x27;casia-entity&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">        prompt_func = entity_extract_prompt</span><br><span class="line">    elif model == &#x27;casia-event&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">        prompt_func = event_extract_prompt</span><br><span class="line">    elif model == &#x27;casia-basic&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">        prompt_func = basic_prompt</span><br><span class="line">    else:</span><br><span class="line">        return &#x27;Illegal model&#x27;, 400</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    if not is_stream:</span><br><span class="line">        if model == &#x27;abstract&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">            prompt, title = prompt_func(input_text)</span><br><span class="line">            response = inference(prompt)</span><br><span class="line">            if title != &#x27;&#x27;:</span><br><span class="line">                flag, response = postprocess(title, response)</span><br><span class="line">                if flag == False:</span><br><span class="line">                    response = &#x27;生成摘要失败，请重新尝试&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">        else:</span><br><span class="line">            prompt = prompt_func(input_text)</span><br><span class="line">            response = inference(prompt)</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">        completion_result = complete_template1(response, received_time, id=&quot;example-completion-1&quot;, object=&quot;text-completion&quot;, model=model, system_fingerprint=&quot;example&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        return_response = Response(json.dumps(completion_result, ensure_ascii=False), mimetype=&#x27;application/json&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">        return return_response</span><br><span class="line">    else:</span><br><span class="line">        prompt = prompt_func(input_text)</span><br><span class="line">        messages = []</span><br><span class="line">        messages.append(&#123;&quot;role&quot;: &quot;user&quot;, &quot;content&quot;: prompt&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">        return Response(generate(messages), mimetype=&#x27;text/event-stream&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></div><footer class="post-footer"><div class="post-ending ending"><div class="ending__text">------ 本文结束，感谢您的阅读 ------</div></div><div class="post-copyright copyright"><div class="copyright-author"><span class="copyright-author__name">本文作者: </span><span class="copyright-author__value"><a href="http://example.com">Yanxudong</a></span></div><div class="copyright-link"><span class="copyright-link__name">本文链接: </span><span class="copyright-link__value"><a href="http://example.com/flask">http://example.com/flask</a></span></div><div class="copyright-notice"><span class="copyright-notice__name">版权声明: </span><span class="copyright-notice__value">本博客所有文章除特别声明外，均采用 <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en" rel="external nofollow" target="_blank">BY-NC-SA</a> 许可协议。转载请注明出处！</span></div></div><div class="post-tags"><span class="post-tags-item"><span class="post-tags-item__icon"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i></span><a class="post-tags-item__link" href="http://example.com/tags/%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/">开发</a></span></div><div class="post-reward